ITestDeviceMutator

public interface ITestDeviceMutator

com.android.tradefed.device.ITestDeviceMutator
Known Indirect Subclasses
TestDeviceMutator
TestDeviceMutator Default implementation of ITestDeviceMutator  

An interface allowing manipulation of the IManagedTestDevice. Note that IManagedTestDevice is not public, ITestDevice is cast to IManagedTestDevice. This is a rather dangerous manipulation and not recommended if you have no need for this.

Summary

abstract void setFastbootEnabled(ITestDevice testDevice, boolean fastbootEnabled)
